description: This file defines the DeviceCommunicationSucceededEvent class, which represents an event indicating successful communication with a device, identified by its eui64 address, in the mock Zigbee core event system.

classes.name: DeviceCommunicationSucceededEvent
classes.description: A class representing an event indicating successful communication with a device, containing the device's EUI-64 identifier.

methods.name: DeviceCommunicationSucceededEvent
methods.description: Constructor for initializing the event with the device's EUI-64 address.

methods.name: getEui64
methods.description: Returns the EUI-64 address associated with this event.
